-463-188813.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 19h00 ng\u00e0y 18/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-421-188810.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-bang-f.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-421-188810.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng chung c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n r\u00fat ra...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>H\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"315","checkdouble":"188823"},{"date":"15:39 18/06","title":"Hotgirl Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh g\u00e2y b\u00e3o tr\u00ean VTV khi n\u00f3i Pele c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi v\u1edbi ... Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hotgirl-cao-diep-anh-gay-bao-tren-vtv-khi-noi-pele-cung-thoi-voi-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh, m\u1ed9t b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3ng xinh \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil - Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u1ee7a VTV \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn fan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1eddi ra n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft khi n\u00f3i xem \u0111\u1ed9i Brazil t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 2000, th\u1eddi c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0... Pele.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng lan truy\u1ec1n m\u1ed9t clip &ldquo;g\u00e2y b\u00e3o&rdquo; khi hotgirl kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham gia ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a VTV &ldquo;ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n&rdquo; kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft&hellip; y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi xem \u0111\u1ed9i Brazil t\u1eeb bao gi\u1edd, b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean: &quot;T\u1eeb khi em c\u00f2n h\u1ecdc c\u1ea5p 1, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 2000, 2002. Th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Ronaldinho, Pele ...&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hotgirl Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh g\u00e2y b\u00e3o khi n\u00f3i Pele c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hotgirl Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh g\u00e2y b\u00e3o khi n\u00f3i Pele c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/1(1).png.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u1ea2nh k\u00e8m n\u1ed9i dung hotgirl trao \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean VTV nhanh ch\u00f3ng lan truy\u1ec1n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng. \u1ea2nh: Internet</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a VTV k\u1ebft th\u00fac, \u0111o\u1ea1n clip c\u00f4 g\u00e1i &ldquo;khoe&rdquo; s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u1edd ngh\u1ec7ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pele \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng lan truy\u1ec1n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Facebook.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Pele n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 2000, 2002 v\u1edbi Ronaldo? \u00d4ng \u1ea5y gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1977 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i m\u1eb9 \u1ea1, con l\u1eady m\u1eb9!&rdquo;, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u group Facebook, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 do qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu n\u00ean b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd gay g\u1eaft. C\u0169ng r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 &quot;truy ra&quot; Facebook c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 g\u00e1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh, sinh n\u0103m 1995.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;T\u1ee9c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 2000, em m\u1edbi 5-6 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e3 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Pele \u0111\u00e1 World Cup h\u1ea3?&quot;, m\u1ed9t fan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u00ecm ra s\u1ef1 phi l\u00fd trong l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cao Diep Anh\" title=\"Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/33.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay, VTV \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn World Cup b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c &ldquo;tung&rdquo; h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t hotgirl kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi xinh \u0111\u1eb9p ng\u1ed3i c\u00f9ng b\u00e0n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y l\u00ean s\u00f3ng, nh\u1eefng &ldquo;b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3ng&rdquo; kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a VTV \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp &ldquo;g\u00e2y b\u00e3o&rdquo; do ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd qu\u00e1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, khi l\u00ean s\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i d\u0103m c\u00e2u ba \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ed3i&hellip; c\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft, kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ch\u00ea c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi qu\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u1ebdo, l\u1ea1c l\u00f5ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i&rdquo; qu\u1ed1c gia.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i n\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-tunisia-va-du-doan-anh-vs-tunisia-421-188828.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Anh vs Tunisia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-sac-nang-wag-noi-bat-nhat-tuyen-bi-o-world-cup-2018-421-188822.html\">Nhan s\u1eafc n\u00e0ng WAG n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-12-nhan-dinh-bang-h-binh-thuong-nhung-kho-luong-421-188818.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 12: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng H &ndash; B\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-421-188810.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dkvd-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-421-188808.html\">\u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c thua s\u1ed1c ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n: Low \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ebft b\u00e0i?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Ictnews.vn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"314","checkdouble":"188824"},{"date":"15:54 18/06","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 HAGL, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau chu\u1ed7i 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i V-League n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB HAGL t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 4 tr\u00ean BXH. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat, \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 \u0111ang m\u1ea5t d\u1ea7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/15590672_1541363012547079_3004420379754663853_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3, HAGL nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua l\u00e0 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh v\u1ea5t \u0111i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang, ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, ph\u1ea7n c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n NHM s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9, c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 HAGL \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n chung c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qua t\u00e2m th\u01b0 n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng T\u1ea5n Anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f9ng BHL \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c, t\u00ednh to\u00e1n b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng HAGL h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean v\u0103n chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\"K\u00ednh g\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua,to\u00e0n th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean HAGL 3 mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc, Trung, Nam \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a, \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eafng, v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xa h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m km \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i.Nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m y\u00eau m\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u \u0111ang sinh s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.\u00a0<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n nay, V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i h\u01a1n 1/2 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng HAGL sau g\u1ea7n 4 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0110o\u00e0n Nguy\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f4n l\u1ee9a U19 l\u00ean s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i V League v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 d\u00e0nh cho nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadn l\u1ef1c, h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m,\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra; ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt xin l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 xin h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u00e8n gi\u0169a, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi trung b\u00ecnh 22, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o n\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t non kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng,nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2m \u201cKh\u00f4ng \u00e9p tr\u00e1i ch\u00edn non\u201d m\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, h\u00e0i h\u00f2a theo t\u00e2m sinh l\u00fd.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng, kinh qua ngh\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh, th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb s\u1ebd r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee9c t\u00ednh khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n trong \u1ee9ng x\u1eed, \u00fd ch\u00ed ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1n trong tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c...<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f9ng BHL \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c, t\u00ednh to\u00e1n b\u1ed5 sung, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Thay m\u1eb7t to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, xin ng\u00e0n l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5m l\u00f2ng y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh cho. Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 ch\u00ednh C\u00f4ng ty S\u1eefa VPMILK-IQLACPRO \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 trang ph\u1ee5c Mizuno, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Next Media...<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1,c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean th\u1ec3 thao, c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Ch\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 </em><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em>World Cup 2018</em></span><em> s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u V-League 2018 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra\".</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-tra-gia-dat-cho-chien-thang-nguoc-dong-truoc-hagl-168-188823.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/15/da-nang-tra-gia-dat-cho-chien-thang-nguoc-dong-truoc-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-tra-gia-dat-cho-chien-thang-nguoc-dong-truoc-hagl-168-188823.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft cho chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL</span><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n, CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo kh\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\">HLV HAGL th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu sau tr\u1eadn thua SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\">HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec5m nh\u1eefng t\u1eadt x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL (V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"313","checkdouble":"188827"},{"date":"16:14 18/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Anh vs Tunisia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-tunisia-va-du-doan-anh-vs-tunisia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 \u201cc\u1ea3 gan\u201d \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i thi\u00ean m\u1ec7nh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:</em> Anh vs Tunisia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>1h ng\u00e0y 19/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Volgograd Arena (th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Volgograd)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Anh 0.91 *0:1*-0.96 Tunisia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u -0.94*2 1/4*0.87 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-tunisia-va-du-doan-anh-vs-tunisia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia 1h ng\u00e0y 19/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nAnh kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/4-van-de-ton-dong-o-dt-anh-truoc-ngay-ra-quan-world-cup-2018-421-187989.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate</span> l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. 10 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Tam s\u01b0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea7y y\u00ean t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Anh ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n hi\u1ebfm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Euro 2016, \u0110T Anh d\u01b0\u1edbi tay HLV Roy Hodgson \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ra sao? H\u1ecd h\u00f2a 2/3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thua nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 Iceland 1-2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eric Dier hay Jordan Henderson cho DT Anh tai World Cup 2018?\" title=\"Eric Dier hay Jordan Henderson cho \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/5-cau-hoi-cho-doi-tuyen-Anh-truoc-tran-ra-quan-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2014, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh Hodgson c\u00f9ng Anh b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 4 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n khi giao h\u1eefu. Nh\u01b0ng khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 thua li\u1ec1n 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia, Urguay \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Costa Rica, h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t h\u1ed3n v\u00e0 b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, tr\u01b0\u1edbc Euro 2012, Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ebft Na Uy t\u1edbi B\u1ec9 khi giao h\u1eefu. R\u1ed3i r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, Tam s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Hodgson c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8 (thua Italia sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m). C\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e2m tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 d\u1ec5 \u0111o\u00e1n. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi song \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tay Ban Nha 1-0 Tunisia Thiago\" title=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1-0 Tunisia Thiago\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/10/DfRuwodXkAASmET.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tunisia (tr\u00e1i) c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Tony Adams \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i \u00fd: \u0110T Anh ch\u1eb3ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Tottenham. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng \u1edf m\u1ee9c ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Tottenham v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Danny Rose c\u00f2n 50/50, nh\u1eefng Kieran Trippier, Dele Alli, Eric Dier, Harry Kane \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f3 thay th\u1ebf. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Kyle Walker t\u1eebng c\u00f3 8 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Spurs. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd l\u1edbn song v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alli DT Anh\" title=\"Alli \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/chat-brazil-duy-nhat-trong-doi-tuyen-anh-nam-o-ai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T&nbsp;Anh d\u1ef1a nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Tottenham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, Tunisia t\u1ef1 tin kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m g\u00ec so v\u1edbi Anh. 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng v\u00f9ng Carthage&rdquo; ch\u1ec9 thua \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi TBN, Tunisia ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m duy nh\u1ea5t 1 l\u1ea7n tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch ph\u00fat 84. Kh\u00f4ng may, c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Iago Aspas ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m l\u1ea1i \u0111i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nabil Maaloul th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng h\u00e0nh trang \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Tunisia t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi World Cup 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, h\u1ecd h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Anh gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Khan hi\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh 5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, \u0110T Anh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho Tam s\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n thua sau 8 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Rose hay Ashley Young cho DT Anh tai World Cup 2018?\" title=\"Danny Rose hay Ashley Young cho \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Mourinho-tin-DT-Anh-se-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-tai-Nga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T&nbsp;Anh h\u01b0\u1edbng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Costa Rica, Nigeria, Lithuania r\u1ed3i Slovenia, Tam s\u01b0 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 8 b\u00e0n. Anh ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/doi-truong-harry-kane-noi-gi-truoc-tran-ra-quan-cua-dt-anh-421-188730.html\" target=\"_blank\">ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Harry Kane</span> v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t khi t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp, h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft Tunisia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0 ng\